  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human woman of early middle years, bearing brown eyes set beneath heavy lids and a direct, appraising gaze. Brown hair is kept in a practical, close-bound style that exposes a square jaw and a prominent nose shaped by old breaks. Taupe skin shows ingrained stain at the fingers and faint heat-marks along the forearms, consistent with a life spent at a busy tap. The voice carries the measured cadence of regulated houses, and the expression settles into an even, serviceable neutrality suited to steady trade.",
